data.description: Sprawling, well-built, beautiful 3-sided brick ranch home with a huge, finished basement. Located in the sought-after White Oak Golfing Community in Newnan Ga. Looking for SF, privacy, and great entertainment space, then look no further. This house has so many great features I had to bullet point them so non would be missed:  • Neighborhood features - Homeowners are never short of surrounding beauty with mature pines, dogwoods, azaleas, and a manicured rolling green golf course. Close to everything, 2 short minutes from shopping and great restaurants. 1.5 miles from I-85 and 35 minutes from Hartfield Airport.   • Interior Features – A spacious foyer that opens to a large family room, a grand dining room and a huge eat-in kitchen with plenty of cabinet space. Huge secondary bedrooms with loads of closet space. The home comes complete with a large master suite with a large walk-in closet and plenty of storage shelves. A private screened in porch is right off the master and has amazing views, perfect for bird watching in the morning or star gazing at night. The master bath was renovated in 2021 and is full of upgrades.   • The massive kitchen has long lengthy countertops and lots of cabinet space. The kitchen opens to a deck on the right side and a screened in porch on the left side, and new carpet has been installed throughout the main level.   • Basement – The basement is like a second home. Complete with a full kitchen, a large family room, a huge bedroom and a full bathroom and a half bath for guests. Again, the sf in this house is impressive and the views to the secluded backyard and golf course is just right for nature lovers.    • Exterior Features – 3 large patios and a huge deck, all perfect for entertaining or just relaxing taking in the surrounding beauty of nature and the golf course. This property has an extended circular driveway that offers plenty of parking space.
